30:24.448 --> 30:26.564
[ringing]

30:31.038 --> 30:33.700
[woman]
Hello? Hello?

30:33.916 --> 30:35.998
Anyone there?
Hello?

30:37.878 --> 30:39.254
[scoffs]

30:42.800 --> 30:47.009
J‘J‘ Some good loving with me J‘J‘

30:47.221 --> 30:50.588
J‘J‘ Some good loving with me J‘J‘

30:51.559 --> 30:54.346
J‘J‘ Some good loving J‘J‘

