-|t's the assault, isn't it?

55:30.286 --> 55:33.278
It must have come up in your
background checks. I get it.

55:33.498 --> 55:36.205
Last deputy didn't respond
too well when he got shot.

55:36.417 --> 55:38.794
No. No, he didn't.

55:43.841 --> 55:46.332
You mind talking about
what happened to you...

55:48.971 --> 55:50.427
...four years ago?

55:53.476 --> 55:54.932
Yeah, uh...

55:57.188 --> 55:58.394
Um...

55:59.899 --> 56:02.106
My brother Phil and l

56:02.318 --> 56:05.025
