from shooting Lennie?

57:51.135 --> 57:52.671
I think George shot Lennie

57:52.887 --> 57:54.969
'cause he felt it was
the only option he had left.

57:56.057 --> 57:58.764
I'd like to get there
before things ever got that bad.

58:26.545 --> 58:28.285
[door slams]

58:30.883 --> 58:31.963
How about Monday?

58:32.176 --> 58:33.757
For what?

58:33.970 --> 58:35.551
First day on the job.

58:36.389 --> 58:39.096
Yeah, Monday works for me.

58:44.313 --> 58:49.228
